				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you have 512 free bytes -- you can't get much faster than a LUT
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">divide_by_15:<br />&nbsp; LDX divisor<br />&nbsp; LDA division15_table,X<br />&nbsp; STA quotient<br />&nbsp; LDA remainder15_table,X<br />&nbsp; STA remainder<br />&nbsp; RTS<br /></div>
<br />
<br />
<br />EDIT
<br />
<br />Even if you need to divide a 16-bit number, you can run the high and low bytes through the LUT, then combine the results.... then run the remainder through the LUT and combine it.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

